==Korean==
===Noun===
'''겨리''' (gyeori)
# [[plough]] drawn by the two [[yoke]]d draft animals

====Antonyms====
* [[호리]] (hori) [[plough]] drawn by '''one''' draft animal instead of the '''two''' yoked. 

====Derived terms====
* 겨리[[질]] (gyeori-jil) [[deal]] with the two yoked draft animals (as in ploughing) 
* 겨릿[[소]] (gyeoris-so) yoked cows

====Related terms====
* [[겨드랑이]] (gyeodeurangI) [[armpit]]
* [[겨레]] (gyeore) [[german]] , [[kinsfolk]], [[race]], [[relatives]], [[sib]] 
* [[겨를]] (gyeoreul) [[free time]] (after work)
* [[겨루다]] (gyeoruda) To [[compete]]
* [[결]] (gyeol) [[vicinity]], [[layer]]
* [[곁]] (gyeot) [[side]], [[vicinity]]
* [[켜]] (kyeo) [[layer]], [[ply]]
* [[켤레]] (kyeolle) [[pair]], [[conjugation]]

